  "subject": "[DCAEGEN2] Improve kubernetes probes",
  "commit_message": "[DCAEGEN2] Improve kubernetes probes\n\n- replace initialDelaySeconds with startup probes\n- shorten probe intervals to 10 seconds\n- fix instances where timeoutSeconds > periodSeconds\n- expose datalake admin ui via httproute\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-3389\nChange-Id: I3145ef4d1c979b0a11264ff64c7d7109ac9894fa\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
